    "These topics include updates to privacy policies, security measures, the purpose of using information, functional cookies, third-party hyperlinks, and the potential requirement to disclose information to law enforcement authorities.",
    "Regarding the effects of CCPA/CPRA enforcement, we found that more topics in relation to these regulations have been included since December 2019.",
    "This supports our previous observation in Section 5.2.2, a significant increase of phrases in privacy policies referring to CCPA/CPRA-related rights.",
    "Figure 4 shows this upward trend for CCPA/CPRA-related topics that include core principles of these laws, such as the option to opt out of the sale of personal information, response time and format of verifiable consumer requests, and individual rights of Californians.",
    "A concerning trend is the continuous rise of referrals to \"legitimate interests\" also found in prior work [76]."
